title: S1, E7: Real As F**k
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary: Things just got real. Molly may have finally dug herself into a hole she can’t get out of and Issa got plummeted off her high horse. Our besties can’t even lean on each other because they just had the most intense exchange of low blows. Episode 7 had a lot of OMG moments,--Crissle and Fran tackle it all in the latest recap of HBO’s Insecure.
